parameters:
\SE\SE[90]So this is how it's all connected. \!\SE[90]I
finally made it back...

\SE[7]Good work. \SE\SE[0]I will deliver this to King
Ulyssean. \SE[0]You can rest first.

\SE[31]Haa... Onee-san, she's so kind... \SE[1]I really love
the fish dishes from Ulyssean. \SE[15]Shall we go to the
tavern right away?

\SE[2]Huh? What are you saying? \SE[90]Of course you're
going with me. \SE[2]And besides, you'll end up getting
caught for illegal entry again.

\SE[22]Hey Luna. Let's go eat dessert, okay? \SE[28]I've
been craving the Triple Layer Tiramisu for so long...!

\SE[84]Um... I'm sorry, Laura. Can I borrow this too?
\SE[3]Look, I need someone who can prove our identity...

\SE[8]Laura... Don't be down, okay? \!\SE[1]If it's All-You-
Can- Eat Super Deluxe Beef Bowl... I'll go with you...?

\SE[12]I'm going to eat...! \!\SE[93]I'm going to eat until
I can't eat anymore...!!

\SE[6]I-I'm sorry...? \SE[21]I'll make it up to you next
time...

\SE[2]Ah... I can see the city walls... \!\SE[3]Is this
Ulyssean...?

\SE[2]Yes, that's right. \SE[0]...Although, it's my first
time coming here too.

\SE[5]Is that so...? \SM[double]\SE[21]Then let's go
sightseeing once we settle down. I'm sure it'll be fun.

\SE\SE[15]That sounds nice. \SE[15]Hehe... It seems like a
lot of fun.

Welcome to Ulyssean. Are you here for immigration? I
apologize for the intrusion, but may I ask where you are
from?

Hatayaki Village... I understand your situation. Currently,
Ulyssean is accepting refugees. I apologize for the
inconvenience, but please submit your application at the
Guild later.

Wait, the person behind you. That outfit... It's the Black
Uniform of Codain, isn't it?

Currently, Ulyssean and Codain are in a state of cold war.
\! Can you please accompany me to the headquarters for a
more accurate identification?
